==Novels==
[[File:Bogart and Bacall The Big Sleep.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Humphrey Bogart]] as [[Philip Marlowe]], with [[Lauren Bacall]] in the 1946 film ''[[The Big Sleep (1946 film)|The Big Sleep]]]]

Chandler left an unfinished novel when he died. This was completed by [[Robert B. Parker]] and published in 1989 as ''[[Poodle Springs]]''.<ref name="Guard: PS" />

